snippet.title: Geometry - Inscribed Angles
snippet.description:
The MathemaGYPTIAN is back with a video on inscribed angles in circles. The lesson begins and ends with a free-style rap, and in between we solve four circles for their inscribed angles. Great interaction and learning today, YAY MATH!
Please visit yaymath.org
